lead_paragraph: Michelle Wie was stung by a bee Thursday in the season-opening Pure Silk-Bahamas LPGA Classic, and second-ranked Inbee Park withdrew because of back pain after the second-worst round of her LPGA Tour career.

headline.print_headline: Michelle Wie Stung by Bee in LPGA Tour Opener in Bahamas
